        <abstract>
            As an integrated part of an on-going survey programme for vegetation mapping, plant species have been recorded. This dataset contains 18 521 registrations of plants from 1190 different circular plots throughout Norway. All species localities are georeferenced, the spatial uncertainty is provided, and additional ecological information is reported.
        </abstract>
